{"tid":797601,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"到底伯母有幾好呃","createTime":"2018-08-28T15:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T16:30:04.000Z","uid":132243,"like":62,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9280f1aaedf7b0796ddde8779463d38012416336","tid":797601,"uid":132243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T15:34:43.000Z","msg":"姐係你地娘親<br />\n<br />\n話說前幾日去完D一日旅行<br />\n三百幾蚊買左套茶具返黎<br />\n好醒咁話真係紫砂茶具黎，仲要限量18套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有一次佢話見到減價，問佢死都唔肯講邊到<br />\n買左四十支韓國牌子牙膏返黎，到而家都仲用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有一次中聯辦打比佢，佢拎住副身家行左兩個鐘先發現比人呃緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654f81be3b101fcc23f3aa4328d3f4937eba5100","tid":797601,"uid":61974,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:06:27.000Z","msg":"為什麼窮人永遠無法翻身？因為整天都在追逐沒用的「佔便宜」快感<br />\n<br />\n即刻諗起呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874d35181e3f70d63703a7615a51377669879650","tid":797601,"uid":92690,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T21:20:30.000Z","msg":"對住屋企人永遠乜都抱住懷疑心態，但對外人俾佢呃左都話個外人老實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fe1acdbccc52577554db13cf56e9aba8fe72fe","tid":797601,"uid":615,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T00:21:29.000Z","msg":"生到個仔咁醒 ，但伯母就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d012f20d2e17c5387c